[50.903613, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[1;31m\u001b[1m5 of 5 artifacts carry contains_pii\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mnobody declared this. it followed the data.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[50.915917, "o", "\r\n"]
[53.928007, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Five artifacts. One declaration. The tag followed the data, not a config.”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “That's a blast radius — and it's the answer to 'which models are affected?'”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[53.928251, "o", "\r\n"]
[56.940596, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “And it's not a guess. Ask the model why it's tainted, and it shows its work.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[56.94087, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ roar tag why contains_pii model.pkl\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[57.265968, "o", "Why does model.pkl have contains_pii?\r\n  model.pkl: contains_pii=present — inherited via job ebc144ed\r\n      └─ test.csv: contains_pii=present — inherited via job 4f247137\r\n          └─ raw.csv: contains_pii=present — user `roar run --add-tag` in job 3f63af7e (session-scoped)\r\n      └─ train.csv: contains_pii=present — inherited via job 4f247137\r\n          └─ raw.csv: contains_pii=present — user `roar run --add-tag` in job 3f63af7e (session-scoped)\r\n"]
[57.296345, "o", "\r\n"]
